HEADWORD: Morse
<hw>Morse</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>morse</ets>,
Russ. <ets>morj'</ets>; perh. akin to E. <ets>mere</ets> lake; cf. Russ.
<ets>more</ets> sea.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The walrus. See
<er>Walrus</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

