==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Morse
<hw>Morse</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>morsus</ets> a biting, a
clasp, fr. <ets>mordere</ets> to bite.]</ety> <def>A clasp for fastening
garments in front.</def> <rj><au>Fairholt.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

